snippet.title: F.SCT Story Lobby BGM Piano Performance / Theme142 "Encroached Sky" / Blue archive Final Chapter OST
snippet.description:
Blue Archive Final Chapter OST - "Theme 142" 「Encroached Sky」 Piano Performance


Today's performance is BGM appearing in the lobby of the final story chapter.
This is "Theme 142: Encroached Sky".

I wanted to upload it when the final chapter was updated, but It's a little late because I'm working on another piece.

Original song with attractive beats, bass and samples
How about putting a piano on it and playing it together? I worked with a heart.

I made some new lines without harming the original song too much.
Samples used existing ones, and also arranged & played as briquettes.

Thank you for listening.

---------------------------------------------------
Discord Channel : https://discord.gg/TGvwJR9rs7
Twitch Streaming : https://www.twitch.tv/frost_piano

Blue Archive 1st Anniversary PV OST(Luminous Memory) Piano Play : https://youtu.be/1xhW91bbFS8
[1st Anniversary] Blue Archive 「Target For Love」 Piano & Guitar Ver. : https://youtu.be/fC7HWUYQLdQ

템플릿 : 론박자막연구소
